Minette Walters

Acid Row

London: Macmillan, 2001. First edition, first printing. Hardcover.

Crisp stated first U.K. edition, first print signed by the author on the title page. Book shows no former owner or remainder marks. Pages are VERY lightly age-toned to the edges. Great reading copy.

Dust jacket is not price clipped and it's crisp, clean and blemish-free. Fine condition.

Reading copy / Fine. Item #96
